        'meta_description' => 'A three-day Mactan honeymoon for Cebu-flying couples: Hilutungan and Caohagan island hop, Cebu heritage afternoon, sutukil dinner. Calm, couple-paced.',
        'tags' => 'Mactan, Honeymoon, Cebu, Island Hopping, Couple Travel',
