        'meta_title' => 'Multigen Family Reunion in Tagaytay: Three-Day Plan | Resort Guru PH',
        'meta_description' => 'A three-day Tagaytay family reunion plan: Sky Ranch for the kids, Caleruega for the elders, Picnic Grove photos, and ridge buffet dinners.',
        'tags' => 'Tagaytay, Family Reunion, Multigenerational Travel, Manila Escape, Group Trip',
