        'meta_title' => 'Couples Five-Day Boracay: Day-by-Day Itinerary | Resort Guru PH',
        'meta_description' => 'A five-day Boracay couple plan: Station 1 base, private island hopping, Mount Luho, Bulabog sunrise, helmet diving. Day-by-day couple itinerary.',
